description:
Hello, my name is Joe Seliskar. This is my final portfolio (for Professor Young). If for some reason you haven't viewed my website that contains my "welcome blurb," "image that represents me" (it's the background picture of the statue), and my project narrative, please follow the link below.

If the game doesn't work for some reason, the website also has copies of all of the required materials that you would otherwise find in the game. Thank you for playing!
